Title: Miss Pouty Lip Plumping(Red)
Description: The Miss Pouty lip pump suction cup lip enhancer works by using self-suction to enhance your lip line and give added fullness. It takes some practice to achieve the best look for your lips using Miss Pouty. With practice you will see what placements add the most fullness. Wetting the area around the mouth helps get the best suction.Position the enhancer over the mouth area and begin to gently suck in, creating a firm suction.Gently continue until you feel your lips and the area around your lips pull into the Miss Pouty enhancer. Start slowly, sucking gently and creating a suction, and release the suction after about 10-15 seconds.Continue with the enhancer and keep checking to see if you have your desired look and fullness. If not, repeat all of the above steps.Using your Miss Pouty enhancer should NOT hurt, if it hurts, then you have created too much of a suction, so use your tongue or your finger and break the suction. You can then replace the enhancer and begin again. Stop immediately if you get bruising. Using the round, large enhancer, your whole mouth area will be encompassed. If you are using one of the ovals, you can target specific areas to enlarge. The ovals can be used horizontally or vertically. When using vertically, place the enhancer in the centre of your lip area, covering both your top lip and bottom lip, this will increase the middle area of your lips, giving a more cupid look to the lip line. You can also move this from side to side, doing the side areas of the mouth. Using the oval horizontally, you can focus on either the top or bottom lip or both.

Title: VolumOn Professional Building Fibre - Keratin M-024 Extreme Hair Volumizer Keratin Fibers(28 g)
Description: Volumon keratin fibres utilises the latest technology to ensure the thickest, textured and natural keratin hair solution. It is a cosmetic breakthrough which immediately transforms your appearance, leaving men and women with thicker looking hair in under 30 seconds. The fibres are electro statically charged, creating a magnetic effect, binding them to existing hair cells, thus maximising their holding potential. They product dramatic density with volume and totally undetectable coverage to your thinning and balding areas.Volumon Keratin Hair Fibres use the highest quality, pure organic keratin, which is the most similar to protein found in humans. This provides the most realistic and textured artificial hair solution. The results are so dense and natural, that it is impossible to detect any artificial fibres, even at close range.Volumon's keratin hair fibre formula is so effective, that the fibres are resistant to wind, rain and perspiration, yet they easily wash out with shampoo.The fibres attach to your existing hair, which creates a strong hold which lasts all day.Volumon keratin hair fibres can be used on all types and shades of hair. Whether it is black, brown or blonde, shorty, curly or long, the results will remain outstanding. Even at close range it is impossible to detect the hair fibres, because they do not spear or stain, but provide a natural, thick and textured appearance.Hairloss can have an enormously negative effect on our self esteem and confidence. Volumon's hair fibres have helped positively change the lives of millions of men and women accross the globe, from those suffering from alopecia, from those experiencing thinning hair, or even drastic baldness.

Title: L'Oreal Paris colour riche lipstick 2.9 g(Fiery Veil)
Description: it's smooth, moisturizing, and easy to apply. It doesn?t dry out my lips as the day goes on, and even after the color fades. Enriched with Vitamin E to provide Moisturisation and Comfort to Your Lips. Brings Your Lips Alive With a Rich, Shiny and Dazzling Colour

Title: D&G Intense EDP  -  100 ml
Description: D&G reveals the sheer charm of the confident and chic woman with this potent fragrance that is subtle and intoxicating to the hilt. Oriental Floral Fragrance Be a head-turner when you dab this Oriental Floral Fragrance and step out as the aroma is glorious and uplifts your charm. Intense Full-bodied Feminine Signature An intense full-bodied feminine signature, Intense Eau de Parfum is extremely captivating and has an enchanting aroma that impresses those around you and lets you steal those second glances.

Title: Colour Me Purple EDT  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Colour Me Purple Womens Perfume 100ml Brand: Colour Me Top: Watery, Floral Middle: Rose, Jasmin, Fruity Dry down: Woody, Vanillic Genealogy: Chypre-Fruity Gender: Female Fragrance Description An elegant rich modern fruity chypre fragrance. The fresh top notes of bergamot and watermelon are boosted by a subtle floral accord of pretty jasmin, rose and violet notes. The dry down is a tenacious blend of oakmoss, amber and precious patchouli woods. 100mle 3.4fl.oz

Title: Diesel Green EDT  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: The long-lasting, scintillating fragrance will surely turn many heads around. You can also gift it to a dear one! Refreshing and rejuvenating, this perfume is a catch!

Title: Giorgio Armani Onde Vertige EDP  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Onde Vertige by Giorgio Armani is a woody aromatic fragrance for women. Onde Vertige is a new fragrance and it was introduced in 2008. The fragrance features frangipani, licorice, patchouli, jasmine and pitosporum.

Title: Estee Lauder Pleasures EDC  -  50 ml
Description: A fragrant entanglement of refreshing notes, keeps you refreshed all day long, Makes a subtle yet bold impression.

Title: Ghost Man EDT  -  100 ml
Description: Have you ever dreamt of playing the role of a ghost, Ghost Man Advanced will give you the unique chance and an adrenaline buzz as well. Travelling through the night sinister maze in search of delicious morsels of food, please, beware of greenlobster-eyed ghosts shuttlecocking near you: if once they bite your neck, you will lose your ghosts life at its early beginning! The main goal is to grab all the morsels before the other ghosts catch you. Play this captivating arcade game free right now.

Title: Jean Paul Gaultier Koko Rico EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: A woody aromatic fragrance for menCrisp, masculine, and strongTop notes of fig leavesHeart notes of raw cocoaPatchouli, cedar and vetiver Base notes?Launched in September 2011Suitable for all occasions

Title: Calvin Klein One EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Cool. Clean. Refreshing, CK ONE is the original “shared” fragrance that inspires the confidence to be yourself and encourages you to connect with others. The brand belongs to everyone. CK one is an accessible, universal and easy scent.

Title: Bogner Snow Natural Spray EDT  -  100 ml
Description: Bogner Snow Man is launched in 2000. Top notes: tangerine, galbanum, fig and juniper berries. Heart: lily of the valley, cedar, vetiver, pepper and cassis. Base: oak moss and amber.

Title: Ed Hardy Love & Luck EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Love and Luck for Men from the eponymous brand of tattoo king Don Ed Hardy, seeks inspiration in the vibrant night life of Tokyo City. Defined by its light transparency, this eclectic Eau de Toilette was originally developed by perfumer Olliver Gilloti, and is perfectly in accord with the artistic style of Ed Hardy designs. Specially concocted for the young at heart, Love and Luck for Men rejuvenates you in the long months of summer with its fougere fragrance. A refreshing citrusy accord makes up the top note, with essences of bergamot, orange, cardamom and mandarin. With accords of heady absinthe, cypress, violet and sage, the heart note continues the strain of fresh fruitiness. A woody base note of cedar, dark vetiver, musk and agarwood complements the subtle herbal-green aroma. Enclosed in a painted vial designed with a card game motif and inscribed with the words - Love is a game, this kitschy bottle of energy is emblematic of a man who plays to win.

Title: Paris Hilton Heiress EDP  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Heiress from the fashion house of Paris Hilton infuses myriad hues of fruity and floral essences into an accord that is emblematic of poised sensuality and glamour. Inspired by Paris Hilton herself - heiress to the Hilton fortune, this exotic Eau de Perfume is a charmingly flirtatious embodiment of cool youthful energy. Refreshing and exciting at the same time, Heiress is opulent luxury encased in a bottle, with an invigorating aroma that seduces you with its mysterious magnetism. The exhilarating top note opens with accords of passion fruit, succulent orange, peach granite and delicious champagne mimosa. The sparkling heart note of tiare lily, star jasmine, sweet honeysuckle, grenadine and the pleasing aroma of candied ylang-ylang, is perfectly complimented by a sheer floral base note of violet leaf, vetiver, Tahiti tonka and blonde woods. Adroitly blended and artistically bottled by Henry de Monclin, this sparkling and bright fragrance is an essential expression of feminine chic, unquestionably meant for the heiress in you.

Title: Joop Splash Summer Ticket EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: A woody aquatic fragrance for men Fresh, clean, oceanic & uplifting Top notes are citrusy flavors of lemon & coriander Heart notes of violet leaf accord & Calypsone molecule Base notes of cedar wood & labdanum Launched in 2012 Recommended for summer occasions.

Title: Loofah Loofah White
Description: This self-scented sponge is extremely hygienic, made of hypo-allergenic material and always clean. Just rinse it under running water to eliminate any trace of soap. The sponge remains soft and makes taking a bath relaxing. It is perfect for cleansing your body and exfoliating skin. A gentle rub is enough to stimulate the capillary microcirculation. When used together with soap, the sponge becomes a splendid ball of foam and renders the skin soft and clean. Children can use it easily and have fun while washing themselves.

Title: Vibes Herbal Body Bath Sponge Loofah Pack of 2
Description: Embrace and experience a luxurious way of bathing with the Vibes loofah bath sponge. Made with 100% biodegradable, natural and renewable materials, this bath brush has many beneficial qualities. The outermost layer of our skin generally sheds dead skin cells on a daily basis and without proper exfoliation this dead skin build-up turns the skin dull and ashy. With this bath brush you can gently remove this build-up from the surface of your skin. Not only will this help to improve the look of your skin, it will also get rid of any grime, oil or bacteria. And if you happen to have dry skin, this handy brush will delicately remove any dry flakes from all over your body.Body brushing during bathing is also an age old therapeutic practice. The process will increase your blood circulation, slow down the signs and effects of ageing on your skin and it will even relax the sore muscles in your body. And that’s not all. It will also help to effectively remove all the black and white heads from the surface of your skin and also loosen blockages that cause the growth of ingrown hair.•Help to remove the dead skin cells in a natural way •Increase the blood circulation •Regular exfoliation keeps your skin looking radiant and healthy•Relax the sore muscles •Slow down the sigh of ageing on your skinMaintaining Loofha: •Wet the Vibes completely before using it. •Rinse it in a water and hang it for drying after both. •Change to new loofha scrub after every 3 to 4 weeks

And if you happen to have dry skin, this handy brush will delicately remove any dry flakes from all over your body.Body brushing during bathing is also an age old therapeutic practice. The process will increase your blood circulation, slow down the signs and effects of ageing on your skin and it will even relax the sore muscles in your body. And that’s not all. It will also help to effectively remove all the black and white heads from the surface of your skin and also loosen blockages that cause the growth of ingrown hair.•Help to remove the dead skin cells in a natural way •Increase the blood circulation •Regular exfoliation keeps your skin looking radiant and healthy•Relax the sore muscles •Slow down the sigh of ageing on your skinMaintaining Loofha: •Wet the Vibes completely before using it. •Rinse it in a water and hang it for drying after both. •Change to new loofha scrub after every 3 to 4 weeks

Title: Aroma World Awcucumbereo
Description: Methods Of Using Natural Essential OilsAromatic Baths: Sprinkle 4-8 Drops Of Essential Oil On To The Water?S Surface After The Bath Has Been Drawn. Agitate The Water To Disperse The Oil. Neat Essences Never Leave A Greasy Tide Mark Due To Their Tiny Molecular Structure. The Effect Of Such Baths Is To Reduce Tension In Body And Mind.Aromatic Toweling: After Washing As Usual, Put 2-3 Drops Of Your Favorite Essential Oil On A Wet Face Cloth Or Sponge; Run It Briskly All Over Your Body. Atomizers: Use A Garden Small Pump Or A Spray Bottle To Disperse The Molecules (Dilute In Rose Water For Best Results) Into The Air In A Fine Mist. Compress: Add About 6 Drops Of Essential Oil To A Bowl Containing About 500 Ml Of Water, As Hot As You Can Comfortably Bear. Place A Small Towel On Top Of The Water. Wring Out The Excess And Place The Towel Over The Area To Be Treated Or Run The Town All Over Your Body. A Compress Is A Valuable Way Of Treating Muscular Pain, Sprains And Bruises As Well As Reducing Pain And Congestion In Internal Organs.Cotton Ball: Add A Few Drops Of Essential Oil Onto Cotton Ball In A Small Bowl, And Let It Slowly Disperse The Essential Oil Into The Air; This Is Suitable For Wardrobes, Travelling, Office Desks And Automobiles.Cream And Shampoo: To Enhance The Therapeutic Effect Of Your Favorite Cream Or Shampoo Add A Drop Of Suitable Essential Oil And Feel The Difference.Diffuser: To Get The Most From Your Essential Oils A Diffuser Is Used To Help Disperse The Molecules Into The Air. This Enables The Body To Use Them As You Breathe In The Wonderful Aromas. Some Use Electricity And Others A Heating Element Or Small Lit Candle Under A Bowl Of Water. In The Bowl Add Water Add A Few Drops Of Your Favorite Essential Oil, The Heat Generated From The Electricity Or A Lit Candle Will Warm The Water And Help Disperse The Oil Molecules Into The Air.Foot And Hand Baths: Sprinkle 5-6 Drops Of The Appropriate Essential Oil In A Bowl Of Lukewarm Water. Soak Feet Or Hands For About 10 Minutes. At The End Of A Tiring Day This Can Be Relaxing And Can Even Alleviate Tension Headaches.Gargles And Mouthwashes: For Sore Throats And Laryngitis Add One Drop Of Sandalwood Or Lemon Or Peppermint Oil To A Glass Containing 2 Teaspoonfuls Of Cider Vinegar. Stir Well To Disperse The Oil, And Then Fill The Glass With Warm Water. Natural Essential Oil Dissolves Better In Cedar Vinegar Than In Water And Also Vinegar Helps Reduce The Build-Up Of Tartar On The Backs Of The Teeth.Inhalations: To Help Clear Nasal Passages When You Have A Cold Or Flu, Put 5-10 Drops Of Essential Oil On Your Handkerchief And Inhale As Required. Essential Oil Can Also Be Sprinkled On Your Pillow To Ease Nasal Congestion And To Aid Restful Sleep.Neat Application: Provided The Skin Is Cooled First Under Cold Running Water For At Least 5 Minutes, Lavender, Eucalyptus, Tea Tree Or Geranium Can Be Applied Neat To Minor Burns And Scalds.Steam Inhalations: Pour 500 Ml Of Near Boiling Water Into A Bowl And Then Add 2-4 Drops Of Essential Oil. Inhale The Vapors For 5-10 Minutes. In Order To Trap The Aromatic Steam More Effectively, Drape A Towel Over Your Head And The Bowl To Form A Tent. Steam Inhalations Helps Relieve Respiratory Problems Or As Deep ?Cleansing Facial.

Title: Moksha Almond Oil Sweet - Cold Pressed(30 ml)
Description: Sweet Almond Carrier Oil has been used as an aromatic-bitter for anorexia, as a digestive tonic, to promote menstruation and to reduce fever and expel worms. It is also used by massage therapists. Sweet Almond Carrier Oil is an excellent emollient and is known for its ability to soften and re-condition the skin. It is rich in proteins, Olein Glyceride Linoleic Acid and Vitamin D, and is considered extremely nourishing - particularly when used regularly. It can be expected to sooth dry skin and irritated areas. Massage therapists should note that it can stain sheets.
